{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/v0-supabase/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"v0\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#v0\" aria-label=\"v0 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://v0.app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">v0</a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Vercel이 만든 AI 기반 UI빌더</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>자연어로 원하는 화면 생성</li>\n<li>React 컴포넌트 + shadcn/ui</li>\n<li>GitHub 연동 가능하며 Vercel로 바로 배포도 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>기술 스택</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Next.js</li>\n<li>shadcn/ui (Tailwind CSS)</li>\n<li>Supabase</li>\n<li>Vercel</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>v0 결과</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">글래스모피즘 스타일로 재고관리 페이지 만들어 줘. 재고 목록은 드래그앤 드롭으로 순서 변경 가능하게.</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; margin-left: 0;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/dface/v0-first.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 152.08333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/a59e9/v0-first.webp 192w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/0ca9f/v0-first.webp 384w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/411c4/v0-first.webp 600w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/3b721/v0-first.png 192w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/66595/v0-first.png 384w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/dface/v0-first.png 600w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/gatsby-archive/static/d6c05b4d94e7353c1cc564a8f98b1f7f/dface/v0-first.png\"\n            alt=\"v0 결과\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>헤더에 각 메뉴가 보이지만 위 대시보드 페이지 하나만 생성<br>\n→ 사용할 메뉴[대시보드/재고/카테고리 설정] 수정 후 직접 페이지 추가</li>\n<li>mock 데이터라 실제 입력, 수정, 삭제할 수 있도록 재요청<br>\n→ Supabase연결 후 CRUD 구현</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"v0-환경에-추가-작업\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#v0-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%97%90-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80-%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85\" aria-label=\"v0 환경에 추가 작업 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>v0 환경에 추가 작업</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>v0에서 직접 수정하면 연결이 자주 끊기고 노드 모듈도 간헐적으로 인식하지 못해 로컬환경에서 작업</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1. 품목 추가, 품목 수정 팝업은 Radix UI dialog 로 변경</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">modal.tsx</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> Dialog <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@radix-ui/react-dialog'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Root</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">open</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>isOpen<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onOpenChange</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>onOpenChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Portal</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Overlay</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Content</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      ...\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Close</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">asChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Button</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>button<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">variant</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>outline<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          닫기\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Button</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Close</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Content</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Portal</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Dialog.Root</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>2. 카테고리 테이블과 재고 아이템 테이블(아이템의 카테고리) 연결</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Supabase sql로 수정</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TABLE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">IF</span> <span class=\"token operator\">NOT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">EXISTS</span> inventory_items <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n  category_id UUID <span class=\"token operator\">NOT</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">NULL</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">REFERENCES</span> categories<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">UPDATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">CASCADE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DELETE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>3. 재고 상태 탭과 카테고리 탭 추가 (아이템 필터링)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>필터 값을 <code class=\"language-text\">useSearchParams</code>로 받을 때 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Suspense></code> 사용해야함<br>\n(메인에서 바로가기할 경우)</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"tsx\"><pre class=\"language-tsx\"><code class=\"language-tsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">fetchItems</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">setIsItemLoading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> dataItems <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> inventoryApi<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getItems</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setItems</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dataItems<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Fetch Items Error'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">finally</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setIsItemLoading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">InventoryStock</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Suspense</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">fallback</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        로딩 컴포넌트\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">InventoryContent</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Suspense</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>4. UX 개선</h3>\n<h4>재고 테이블</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>아이템 수정 시 각 아이템 별 수정 → 모든 아이템 한번에 수정 후 저장</li>\n<li>드래그 앤 드롭 후 index 저장</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; margin-left: 0;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/fe486/v0-ux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/a59e9/v0-ux.webp 192w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/0ca9f/v0-ux.webp 384w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/dc9b9/v0-ux.webp 768w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/3b721/v0-ux.png 192w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/66595/v0-ux.png 384w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/fe486/v0-ux.png 768w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/gatsby-archive/static/f58e17a7cec52b37d9295654761578d7/fe486/v0-ux.png\"\n            alt=\"v0 ux 수정\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>카테고리</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Line 아이콘 → Solid 아이콘으로 변경\n<ul>\n<li>아이콘에 색상 옵션이 있어 빠르게 인지시키기 위해 솔리드 스타일로 변경</li>\n<li>재고 테이블에서도 카테고리 아이콘 표현</li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-archive/svgr\">SVGR</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>카테고리 아이콘 변경 시 드롭 다운 형태</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 410px; margin-left: 0;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/cb1d0/v0-ux-icon.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.645833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/a59e9/v0-ux-icon.webp 192w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/0ca9f/v0-ux-icon.webp 384w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/a233f/v0-ux-icon.webp 410w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/3b721/v0-ux-icon.png 192w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/66595/v0-ux-icon.png 384w,\n/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/cb1d0/v0-ux-icon.png 410w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/gatsby-archive/static/104c9757d104fad7cbe9b8952e48a978/cb1d0/v0-ux-icon.png\"\n            alt=\"v0 ux 수정\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>* API 레이어 (Supabase Method Chaining 캡슐화)</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">lib/api/inventory.ts</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\">\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> inventoryApi <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token function\">getItems</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> category<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> status<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> search <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> GetItemsParams<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Promise</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>InventoryItem<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> categoryQuery <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> category <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">'*, categories!inner(*)'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'*, categories(*)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> query <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> supabase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">from</span><span 